<FindBugsFilter xmlns="https://github.com/spotbugs/filter/3.0.0">
  <!--
    Reviewed suppressions (Chapter 16: suppress with a reason, never disable a whole detector).

    This module has NONE. The inventory value type (SbomComponent) is an immutable record, the inventory
    returns an immutable List.copyOf snapshot, and the typed exception copies its fields — so the
    representation-exposure detectors (EI_EXPOSE_REP / EI_EXPOSE_REP2) stay quiet without any suppression.
    The filter is kept (empty) so a future, genuinely-reviewed suppression has a home with a reason,
    rather than being added inline. (Distinct from the OWASP Dependency-Check suppressions under
    config/dependency-check/ — that file suppresses third-party CVE findings; this one would suppress
    SpotBugs findings in first-party code. Both follow the same reviewed-with-a-reason discipline.)
  -->
</FindBugsFilter>
